## 2026-05-11 — Content Integration (Lab Hunter)

**Task:** Integrate the "LAB HUNTER - HACKSMATER" write-up.
**Decision:**
- Converted to MDX in `content/pentest-labs/`.
- Moved images to `public/images/content/lab-hunter/`.
- Used `%20` encoding for image URLs in MDX to handle spaces in filenames.
**Reasoning:** Maintain clean repo structure by separating raw docs from production content. `pentest-labs` was the most appropriate category for this web exploitation lab.
**Status:** Active
